        "content": "<p>Does <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/frontier_closed_ball'\">docs#frontier_closed_ball'</a> really need <code>nontrivial E</code>? What fails when <code>E = unit</code>?</p>",
        "id": 278301904,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1649423675
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The closed ball is <code>{0}</code> whose frontier is <code>{0}</code> and the sphere is empty.</p>",
        "id": 278304545,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1649424931
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Isn't the frontier also empty? Both the interior and the closure are {0}.</p>",
        "id": 278306378,
        "sender_full_name": "Junyan Xu",
        "timestamp": 1649425740
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think it is the other way round: boundary is empty, but the sphere is <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\{0\\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">}</span></span></span></span>.</p>",
        "id": 278307959,
        "sender_full_name": "Moritz Doll",
        "timestamp": 1649426353
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yes the sphere is {0} only when r=0. So when E is trivial you must add the condition r \\ne 0.</p>",
        "id": 278308468,
        "sender_full_name": "Junyan Xu",
        "timestamp": 1649426558
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think it is better to have <code>nontrivial E</code>, because nobody cares about trivial normed spaces.</p>",
        "id": 278308698,
        "sender_full_name": "Moritz Doll",
        "timestamp": 1649426644
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Moritz, we have both <span aria-label=\"grinning\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f600\" role=\"img\" title=\"grinning\">:grinning:</span> <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/frontier_closed_ball\">docs#frontier_closed_ball</a></p>",
        "id": 278310566,
